txt.en: This piece of tree-bark is etched with ancient Dunlending writing. It may be a clue as to the origins of the Warg-riders in Carreglyn and should be brought to Gwilum.
'Alas, this is the most disturbing piece of evidence regarding the origin of the Warg-riders you have brought to me yet. I will study this and learn what it may portend.'
'Have you found any evidence regarding the origins of the Warg-riders?'
You found a sheet of tree-bark etched with ancient Dunlending writing.
Bring the rune-marked tree-bark to Gwilum in Barnavon
Gwilum is at the gate to Lower Barnavon.\n\nYou should bring the rune-marked tree-bark to Gwilum.
